            <title>[SOLR-3543] JavaBinLoader catches (and logs) exceptions and the (solrj)client has no idea that an update failed</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3543</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When submitting docs to solr with the javabin wire format server responses with 200 ok even when there was an error. The exception is only logged at the server.&lt;/p&gt;

